<br>
Why bother inventing a RP excuse to twink? But if we must: My level 10 ENC wrote a desperate letter to The Diety Formerly Known as Prince of Hate. The.. let's just call him &quot;&amp;&quot; for short... &amp; was moved deeply by this plea for ubber equipment and empowered the little gnome with the gift of parent selection. The gnome chose 2 lizards, whom were quite accomplished and wealthy, to be his parents. The lizards truely loved their little gift from &amp;, for now they had 160 more inventory slots in which to stuff all maner of lewts and stuff. As time went by, the gnome grew up. When he was nearly 8 hours and 11 seasons old, he declared, &quot;Faction Smaction!, I want to kill something!&quot; His very supportive parents quickly agreed that he could wear anything he wanted, and as soon as he /auctioned off those other 14 trader satchels of gear he should be on his way to seek his own fame and fortune. And thus begins his own story... <p><CENTER>

